- Windows Support 游댯
- TODO support 游
- Git versioning support 游
- Export to other formats (PDF / Word / HTML / Latex) 游
- Rich Email support 游
- Online File Sync 游
- Online collaboration 游
- SSH support (can work over SSH) 游댯
- Support for emoji short-codes 游릭
- Zotero support 游
- TTS support 游
- Hand-drawing support 游

